    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK536">
<l>iḻukkāmai yārmāṭṭu meṉṟum vaḻukkāmai </l>
<l>vāyi ṉaḵtoppa til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is nothing comparable with the possession of unfailing thoughtfulness at all times and towards all persons.</l>
